## Description

{{ agent_description }}

## Environment

- Copy `.env` and set `AGENTVERSE_API_KEY` if you want Agentverse registration (JWT from [Agentverse](https://agentverse.ai)).
- Keep `AGENT_SEED_PHRASE` secret; it is generated for this project.

## Setup

- `make install` — install dependencies with Poetry.

## Running

- `make test` — run the Streamlit test UI (`test.py`).
- `make dev` — run the uAgent locally with `python main.py` (when API keys are not fully configured for hosted deploy).
- `make run` — install, export requirements, and run via Docker Compose (when you are ready for containerized deploy).

The agent uses **uAgents** and the **Agent Chat Protocol** (`uagents_core.contrib.protocols.chat`) for ASI1-compatible chat.
